Bayinya.

538
00:43:39,958 --> 00:43:40,792
Sayang.

539
00:44:02,083 --> 00:44:03,125
Sergio.

540
00:44:10,083 --> 00:44:10,958
Kau sedang apa?

541
00:44:11,042 --> 00:44:14,208
Aku menemukan ponsel.
Sedang mengisi daya. Ada dua bar.

542
00:44:14,875 --> 00:44:17,083
Agak kuno, tapi bisa dipakai.

543
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:29,750
PANGGILAN MASUK

544
00:44:43,875 --> 00:44:44,708
<i>Halo?</i>

545
00:44:46,375 --> 00:44:48,833
- Kau siapa?
