546
00:44:48,917 --> 00:44:50,583
Aku mendukung Profesor dari Asia.

547
00:44:50,667 --> 00:44:53,750
Astaga. Aku Benjamín.

548
00:44:53,833 --> 00:44:54,958
<i>Akan kusambungkan.</i>

549
00:44:55,042 --> 00:44:55,958
Ya, tentu.

550
00:45:01,958 --> 00:45:03,458
