584
00:48:03,458 --> 00:48:05,167
<i>Satu, dua, tiga.</i>

585
00:48:05,750 --> 00:48:06,875
<i>Petak umpet.</i>

586
00:48:08,000 --> 00:48:09,583
<i>Begitulah kejadiannya.</i>

587
00:48:09,667 --> 00:48:11,750
<i>Dalam sekejap kewajaran biasa.</i>

588
00:48:14,833 --> 00:48:17,333
<i>Truk itu menelan sampah.</i>

589
00:48:18,417 --> 00:48:20,042
<i>Tapi lebih dari itu.</i>

590
00:48:22,667 --> 00:48:23,500
Profesor.

591
00:48:23,583 --> 00:48:27,000
<i>Itu membuat otak perampokan</i>
<i>kembali memimpin permainan,</i>

592
00:48:27,500 --> 00:48:29,375
<i>dengan otak baru di sisinya.</i>

593
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:31,000
<i>Yang lebih penting…</i>

594
00:48:35,625 --> 00:48:38,333
